Quest:All the Eels

From Wizard101 Wiki
Jump to: navigation, search

Quest Information


Prequest:
Secret Strife of Pets

Given By: Sohomer Sunblade

Giver Location: Triton Avenue
This is a side quest.

Goals:
Defeat 3 Electric Eels
Talk to Sohomer Sunblade
Hand In: Sohomer Sunblade

Reward:

10
75


Leads to:

Wayward Barrels

Quest Dialogue


This page is for recording a complete Quest Dialogue of all the conversation and story during a quest.
This includes NPC discussions, Narrator statements, and Creature speeches.


Documentation on how to edit this page can be found at Template:QuestInfobox/doc.

Hints, guides, and discussions of the Wiki content related to All the Eels should be placed in the Wiki Page Discussion Forums.

Search for content related to All the Eels in the Central Wiki Forums by clicking here.
